data.description: This 3-bed, 2-bath home boasts an oversized one-car attached garage and oozes character. As you enter, you'll be greeted by stunning hardwood floors that grace the entire space. All bedrooms have carpet. Sitting on a quarter-acre lot within city limits, this property is a canvas for your dreams. Picture building a duplex, parking your RV, cultivating a vibrant garden oasis, and more! Stay cozy and budget-conscious in winter with the efficient forced air gas furnace. Recent updates, including new carpet, fresh paint, and modern lighting just two years ago. Convenience is at your doorstep with nearby city parks, the library, and schools. This adorable single-level home comes complete with an unfinished service basement, promising extra potential and functionality. Call us or your favorite realtor today to see!
